     C**                   MOVELK@KWD2    CTKEY2
     C**                   ADD  1         CTNBR1
     C**                   WRITEAB#PPCT1
     C**                   ENDIF
      **
     C**                   Z-ADDCTNBR1    @@5     50
     C**                   MOVE @@5       @@5C    5
     C**         K@KWD2    CAT  @@5C:0    BARC      P
      **
     C**                   CLEARAB#PP751
     C**                   TIME           WSSDT
     C**                   Z-ADDWSSDAT    PUKODT
     C**                   Z-ADDWSSTM6    PUKOTN
     C**                   MOVEL#USER     PUKOME
     C**                   Z-ADDITOKU     PUCUST
     C**                   Z-ADDINONY     PUNONY
