     C**                   MOVELBARC      PUSERL
     C**                   Z-ADDK@YY      PUNOYY
     C**                   Z-ADDK@MM      PUNOMM
     C**                   Z-ADDK@DD      PUNODD
     C**                   MOVE IODRN     PUODRN
      **
     C**                   WRITEAB#PP751
     C**
     C**                   CLEARAB#PP781
     C**                   TIME           WSSDT
     C**                   Z-ADDWSSDAT    P8KODT
     C**                   Z-ADDWSSTM6    P8KOTM
     C**                   MOVEL#USER     P8KONM
     C**                   Z-ADDITOKU     P8CUST
     C**                   Z-ADDINONY     P8NONY
     C**                   MOVELINKOJ     P8NKOJ
     C**                   MOVELINUKE     P8NUKE
