     C**                   MOVELBARC      P8SERL
     C**                   Z-ADDK@YY      P8NOYY
     C**                   Z-ADDK@MM      P8NOMM
     C**                   Z-ADDK@DD      P8NODD
     C**                   MOVE IODRN     P8ODRN
     C**                   Z-ADDWSSDAT    P8PLDT
     C**                   Z-ADDWSSTM6    P8PLTM
     C**                   MOVEL#USER     P8PLNM
     C**
     C**         K#L7BA    KLIST
