     C**                   KFLD           INKOJ
     C**                   KFLD           INUKE
     C**                   KFLD           K@YY
     C**                   KFLD           K@MM
     C**                   KFLD           K@DD
     C**                   KFLD           K@NOBN  2
     C**                   KFLD           IODRN
     C**                   MOVELINONY     K@NONY
     C**                   MOVELINOTM     K@NOBN
     C**         K#L7BA    CHAINAB#PL7B              90
     C**         *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
